OL,4,G1750FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe last visit of the week is to
OL,6,     GThe Dovecote Inn in
OL,7,     GNottinghamshire, run by Sam and
OL,8,     GSophie. Can their cracking
OL,9,     Gcontinental turn things around
OL,10,     Gafter an underwhelming day out?
OL,11,G1820FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GOn payment day, cutlery quibbles,
OL,13,     Ggrout gripes and breakfast
OL,14,     Gbombshells are debated, before
OL,15,     Gthe payments are revealed and the
OL,16,     Gwinner is announced.
