OL,4,G1850FLocation, Location, Location
OL,5,     GKirstie helps a family who are
OL,6,     Gswapping Switzerland for a new
OL,7,     Ghome in Hove. But they have a
OL,8,     Glong wish list. Phil is with a
OL,9,     Gcouple retiring from Lancashire
OL,10,     Gto the South Downs.
OL,11,G1955FKirstie and Phil's Love It or
OL,12,     FList It
OL,13,     GCan Kirstie breathe new life into
OL,14,     GCarl and Katy's draughty,
OL,15,     Ginefficient Victorian semi with a
OL,16,     Groof-raising renovation? Or will
OL,17,     Gthey be persuaded by pastures new?
